@startuml ContextOS_Event_Driven
skinparam backgroundColor #f8f9fa

title Event-Driven Architecture Diagram

queue "container.exchange\n(Topic)" as CONT_EX
queue "ai.exchange\n(Topic)" as AI_EX
queue "activity.exchange\n(Topic)" as ACT_EX
queue "dead.letter.exchange\n(Direct)" as DLX

queue "container.enrichment\nQueue" as ENR_Q
queue "ai.embedding\nQueue" as EMB_Q
queue "activity.log\nQueue" as ACT_Q
queue "dead.letter\nQueue" as DLQ

rectangle "Producers" {
  [ContainerService] as CONT_SVC
  [SnapshotService] as SNAP_SVC
  [TagService] as TAG_SVC
  [SearchService] as SRCH_SVC
  [UserService] as USER_SVC
}

rectangle "Consumers" {
  [EnrichmentConsumer] as ENR_C
  [EmbeddingConsumer] as EMB_C
  [ActivityConsumer] as ACT_C
  [SearchIndexConsumer] as SRCH_C
}

rectangle "Services" {
  [AIContextService] as AI_CTX
  [EmbeddingService] as EMB_S
  [ActivityService] as ACT_S
  [SearchIndexService] as SRCH_S
}

CONT_SVC --> CONT_EX : container.created\ncontainer.updated\ncontainer.deleted
SNAP_SVC --> CONT_EX : snapshot.created
TAG_SVC --> CONT_EX : tag.assigned\ntag.removed
USER_SVC --> CONT_EX : user.registered\nuser.logged_in

CONT_EX --> ENR_Q : container.#
ENR_Q --> ENR_C : consume
ENR_C --> AI_CTX : enrich
ENR_C --> AI_EX : enrichment.completed

AI_EX --> EMB_Q : embedding.requested
EMB_Q --> EMB_C : consume
EMB_C --> EMB_S : generate embedding

ENR_C --> ACT_EX : activity.#

ACT_EX --> ACT_Q : activity.#
ACT_Q --> ACT_C : consume
ACT_C --> ACT_S : record activity

CONT_EX --> SRCH_Q : container.created\ncontainer.updated
SRCH_Q --> SRCH_C : consume
SRCH_C --> SRCH_S : index for search

== Error Handling ==
ENR_Q --> DLX : after 3 retries
EMB_Q --> DLX : after 2 retries
DLX --> DLQ : dead.letter
DLQ --> DLQ : Monitor for alerts

note right of ENR_Q : x-dead-letter-exchange:\ndead.letter.exchange\nx-message-ttl: 300000
note right of DLQ : Manual replay\nvia admin UI\nAuto-purge after 7 days

@enduml
